<!--
  Auris appcast — host this file at:
  https://headroomstudio.dev/auris/appcast.xml

  How to update for a new release:
  1. Run: make release  →  produces Auris.dmg
  2. Upload Auris.dmg to Cloudflare R2 as Auris-X.Y.dmg, copy the public URL
  3. Get the file size in bytes:  wc -c < Auris.dmg
  4. Sign the DMG with Sparkle:   .build/artifacts/sparkle/Sparkle/bin/sign_update Auris.dmg
     (this prints the edSignature value)
  5. Add a new <item> block at the top (keep old items for reference)
  6. Push to your GitHub Pages repo — Cloudflare picks it up automatically
-->
